name: Sphynx series part1
description: The Canadian hairless cat was created in 1966 by cat lovers in Toronto, Ontario, Canada, from a litter of nearly hairless kittens, through inbreeding, specifically for cat lovers who are allergic to cat hair. This natural genetic mutation gave birth to the Canadian hairless cat we know today. This cat is a kind of body hairless strange breed, some like the famous monster in ancient Egyptian mythology "sphinx", so people named it "Sphinx cat"
